WEBVTT

00:02.835 --> 00:05.637
♪ Boy, the way                  
Glenn Miller played ♪           

00:05.639 --> 00:09.540
             ♪ Songs that made  
             The Hit Parade ♪   

00:09.542 --> 00:12.877
♪ Guys like us                  
We had it made ♪                

00:12.879 --> 00:16.347
    ♪ Those were the days ♪     

00:16.349 --> 00:19.317
           <i>♪ And you knew where</i> 
           <i>You were then ♪</i>      

00:19.319 --> 00:23.622
 <i>♪ Girls were girls</i>             
 <i>And men were men ♪</i>             

00:23.624 --> 00:30.194
  <i>♪ Mister, we could use a man</i>  
   <i>Like Herbert Hoover again ♪</i>  

00:30.196 --> 00:32.363
 <i>♪ Didn't need</i>                  
 <i>No welfare state ♪</i>             

00:32.365 --> 00:36.534
             <i>♪ Everybody pulled</i> 
             <i>His weight ♪</i>       

00:36.536 --> 00:40.805
     <i>♪ Gee, our old LaSalle</i>     
           <i>Ran great ♪</i>          

